Survey.Name: ROSAT Wide Field Camera: F${I}
Survey.Description: This survey is a mosaic of images taken by the ROSAT Wide Field Camera and comprises of 12,743 seperates fields in each of two filters. Each field covers a region 2.6&#176 x 2.6&#176 with a 0.3&#176 overlap. Currently, this data is not a complete coverage of the sky; regions near the northern ecliptic pole are currently not included.
